BitcoinMiner.net contains the latest information on Bitcoin Miner, the Bitcoin mining process, and many other related areas. The site contains information suited for beginners all the way to advanced miners. The site contains some of the most commonly asked questions in regards to why and how you could mine Bitcoin. Information is updated on a daily basis.

Contains lengthily articles that answer questions such as:

What is Bitcoin?
How to Use Exchanges
What is Required to Mine Bitcoin?
What is Bitcoin Difficulty?
What are ASCI's?
What are the Most Popular Mining Pools?
Who are Bitcoin's Largest Miners?
How Much Does Cloud Mining Cost?
How Profitable will Bitcoin Mining Be?

The site discusses both the technical as well as the social aspects of mining Bitcoin.
